description:
Classical and historical literary works from the Project Gutenberg catalog. Full texts are not stored — each atom contains title, author, genre, and a gutenberg.org URL. Where available, Wikipedia summaries (via DBpedia) are used as descriptions.

Default scope: works with classical/literary subject tags in major world languages. Expand with --all for the full 70K catalog.

Atom IDs: lit:work:{title}, lit:author:{name}
